{"tid":1737610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該跑還跑唔好亂推亂撞","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T04:26:21.000Z","uid":9665,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0550d9a8b465d86b6e663abe160aacd8155c580a","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"我係6月到而家都有夢遊習慣既人士，我知道個個都好撚驚，都有好多新手上路，但唔該到你真係要跑既時候，你隻手唔好亂推亂撞，前日就係有咁情況，我見到有2位手足被推跌，唔該所有人同我聽住，你跑既時候係要自己避開障礙物，而唔係推開人等自己跑，你見到有手足跌到or行動不便，你係應該扯佢起身，拉起佢個人，而唔係直行直過，小隊既唔該盡可能捉實自己小隊既人，唔好走散，減少落單既機會，我知道你地好撚驚，但都要保持冷靜，因為你一個人既心態會影響到好多人，唔係叫你慢慢行，而係要保持冷靜，同最撚緊要救人，救人，救人，好緊要所以我講三次，一齊進化，香港人，報仇。"},{"pid":"984c328a5466df054147b91b789e98de1d0c4f66","tid":1737610,"uid":102554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40c05567ff737aeb3d52e0f5b655f1895c7e9f04","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5647ff61136e7a3b56e3d252c10714a07598f06a","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60e6555c76ae5f09b0101ffb83b8850e5900e773","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6003e07970e55e2e75fe7c429ffd0fd4d2f4b1a6","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9d4c3adbde800a83a7321d7fe986a72230bfd947","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"e9109263e7b2181afc79f8453136134f964df04d","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"eea9ee53bfbc5574c33b76f71020919c01bc0913","tid":1737610,"uid":9665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:26:21.000Z","msg":"9"}]}